03900 
03901 #ifndef GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
03902 /* This code block is duplicated in glxext.h, so must be protected */
03903 #define GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
03904 /* Define int32_t, int64_t, and uint64_t types for UST/MSC */
03905 /* (as used in the GL_EXT_timer_query extension). */
03906 #if defined(__STDC_VERSION__) && __STDC_VERSION__ >= 199901L
03907 #include <inttypes.h>
03908 #elif defined(__sun__) || defined(__digital__)
03909 #include <inttypes.h>
03910 #if defined(__STDC__)
03911 #if defined(__arch64__) || defined(_LP64)
03912 typedef long int int64_t;
03913 typedef unsigned long int uint64_t;
03914 #else
03915 typedef long long int int64_t;
03916 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
03917 #endif /* __arch64__ */
03918 #endif /* __STDC__ */
03919 #elif defined( __VMS ) || defined(__sgi)
03920 #include <inttypes.h>
03921 #elif defined(__SCO__) || defined(__USLC__)
03922 #include <stdint.h>
03923 #elif defined(__UNIXOS2__) || defined(__SOL64__)
03924 typedef long int int32_t;
03925 typedef long long int int64_t;
03926 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
03927 #elif defined(_WIN32) && defined(__GNUC__)
03928 #include <stdint.h>
03929 #elif defined(_WIN32)
03930 typedef __int32 int32_t;
03931 typedef __int64 int64_t;
03932 typedef unsigned __int64 uint64_t;
03933 #else
03934 #include <inttypes.h>     /* Fallback option */
03935 #endif
03936 #endif
03937 
03938 #ifndef GL_EXT_timer_query
03939 typedef int64_t GLint64EXT;
03940 typedef uint64_t GLuint64EXT;
03941 #endif
